sequenceDiagram
    actor Agent
    actor HumanReviewer as Human Reviewer
    participant API
    participant Workflow
    participant Task
    participant Policy as Deploy Policy
    participant Audit
    participant Notify as Notification Service
    participant DB

    Agent->>API: Move task to review
    API->>Workflow: Validate transition
    Workflow-->>API: Allowed
    API->>Task: Update status = in_review
    Task->>DB: Save status
    Task->>Audit: Record handoff
    Audit->>DB: Save event
    Task->>Notify: Notify reviewer

    HumanReviewer->>API: Approve review
    API->>Workflow: Validate approval transition
    Workflow-->>API: Allowed
    API->>Policy: Check deployment responsibility
    Policy-->>API: Only human may deploy production
    API->>Task: Update status = ready_to_deploy
    Task->>DB: Save status
    API->>Audit: Record approval + deploy restriction
    Audit->>DB: Save event
